    "ML models, proposed as a powerful tool to capture the unknown synergies between the VNF and its environment, are shown to be suitable for the anomaly detection problem in NFV.",
    "Survey of Existing ApproachesThe use of ML to classify Internet traffic and detect anomalies in Network is widely studied [60,61].",
    "This survey covers the research works that have adapted the ML techniques to suit the VNF environment requirements.",
    "A handful of research papers addressed this problem.",
    "They can be classified into supervised and unsupervised approaches as presented below."
